{"tid":756302,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"張家輝劉青雲再度合作《廉政風雲煙幕》","createTime":"2018-07-26T02:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T10:37:27.000Z","uid":41343,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9848bb3b3fe61e6bbd2a9966468a7026905b1a4c","tid":756302,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:38:44.000Z","msg":"劉青雲、張家輝、湯怡、陳家樂、吳浩康與英皇娛樂老闆楊受成等，今日出席新戲《廉政風雲 煙幕》煞科宴。青雲和家輝五年後再合作，家輝表示跟青雲做對手戲最舒服，每次合作都打開心窗。<br />\n<br />\n青雲透露戲中與林嘉欣對手戲不多，只透過電話隔空與對方鬧交，青雲說：「導演說不可以扯火，要斯文、內斂，那麼深層次，所以要由我來演。」他笑指跟太太郭藹明十分恩愛，不會鬧交，是否難投入角色？青雲笑說：「這是虛偽的表現，我們好少鬧交，因為無乜好講。」<br />\n<br />\n講到家輝在澳洲外景一個月，青雲裝作不滿，他笑說：「我在香港死慳死抵，就畀你去澳洲玩。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20180724/s00009/f546f610a3c81ee6d60d7ad7d817c6f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20180724%2Fs00009%2Ff546f610a3c81ee6d60d7ad7d817c6f6.jpg&h=b25ce6d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23ed7ab3e1b99e678eea80fa4db75b2f2094d0ab","tid":756302,"uid":24007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:40:20.000Z","msg":"今次無送古天樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6db313eed5f20966d596c9c9c991ca016a7314d","tid":756302,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:40:36.000Z","msg":"chur ..."},{"pid":"2ae1b5b18079f8aea8e4c2820a5e1e45331e00f8","tid":756302,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T05:37:24.000Z","msg":"咩風暴？"},{"pid":"10b826f4906a657eb14ffead72844d8338e14822","tid":756302,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23ed7ab3e1b99e678eea80fa4db75b2f2094d0ab","tid":756302,"uid":24007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:40:20.000Z","msg":"今次無送古天樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},